        <num>CCP 4266</num>
        <heading>4266.  Continuation of business</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4266.  Continuation of business
The court may authorize a tutor to continue any business in which the minor has an interest, when it appears to the best interest of the minor, and after compliance with Article 4271.  The order of court may contain such conditions, restrictions, regulations and requirements as the court may direct.</p>
        </content>
